@node "gr3" "CANE Demo"

@{fg shine} CANE Demo@{fg text}

 C.A.N.E stands for Cargo And Nothing Else, the idea is to collect the 
various cargo littered around each level. There are also some little 
`Dudes' which you MUST collect to complete the level.

 This is a two level demo, the full version is not available, due to lack 
of interest, but these levels will take you ages to complete (Well, I 
haven`t completed the first level yet!).

 The levels are two screens big, and when your triangular ship gets near 
the top they scroll which gives the game that really cool look, and lets 
you know this is not your average P.D game.

 To pick up a `dude' or some cargo you mist land on top of it and have your
nose pointing up, this is really difficult especially in water as the 
gravity pulls you up, its easier in the sky as gravity pulls you down. When
you have collected your cargo you must deposit it in your teleporter (where
you start)

 The game is really difficult, if you drop the dude in the water he dies 
and you can`t complete the level! You also have to use bomb and collect 
diving gear to be able to collect some of the cargo!

 This is a brilliant game, if you download this, and like it, perhaps you 
could E-Mail the author and make him continue developing this brilliant 
game. If not, it is a shame this is going to be discontinued.

