@node "gr6" "Lazer"

@{fg shine} Lazer@{fg text}

 The idea behind Lazer is to bounce a laser around the screen and to hit a 
target. To aid you in doing this you are provided some mirrors. There are 
11 mirrors available for all the levels. Obviously you can`t use more than 
11 mirrors but you can use less. The mirrors alos, only reflect on one 
side.

 You are timed and author tells us the levels can be completed! (Yea, 
right!). The first few levels are easy, then you get onto a level where the
lazer will only travel in one direction!

 Lazer is really hard, when you think you`ve done it the computer moves or 
rotates a mirror and you time runs out. Time is tight and the computer is 
really frustrating!

 The sounds in this game are the best i`ve heard in a long time, they 
really make you want to laugh sometimes!

 The game plays well, the lastability end-less, this is all most as good as
Final Odyssey!! I definatly what to see more of effots from this author!

