@node "gr9" "NeverMind"

@{fg shine} NeverMind@{fg text}

 I was going to review this in the last issue, but due to disk problems I 
wasn`t able to, so I downloaded this off the Aminet, and it is still in the
Recent uploads!

 The idea is to reach the exit by avoiding all the mines in the mine field,
which is the screen around you. When you move you are told how many mines 
are around you. If you uncover a ? square, which could have bomb underneith
them you gain points, but when you move back over a square you have 
already uncovered you lose some points!

 The game is quite hard, even in beginner mode! I have only actually 
completed it once in about 30 odd games!

 There are several options, first off is your skill level, from beginner to
expert, then theres your screenmode, theres not really much point to this, 
